Introduction

Aila was a four-member girl group under Plane Entertainment. The group consisted of Kelly, Siyeon, Rahee, and Yena.

They debuted on January 15, 2014 with the single "Pretty Pretty Pretty Girl" and disbanded sometime later the same year.
